	                        </ul>
	                    </li>
	                    <li>
	                        <a href="/donation">후원하기</a>
	                    </li>
	                </ul>
                </div>
			</div>
		</nav>
		<div id="container">
			<div id="container1">
				<div class="slider">
					<div class="item1">
						<div class="background"></div>
						<div class="text-block f1-under">
							<p>
								<strong class="f1">잊혀져 가는 과거의 <br />일면을 되새기며</strong> 당신을 기억합니다.<br /> 기억하고 있습니다.<br /> 잊지않고 있습니다.
							</p>
							<div class="btn">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="item2">
						<div class="background"></div>
						<div class="text-block v2">
							<p>
								<strong class="f1">아시아 태평양<br /> 평화교류협회 출판회</strong>
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div id="m_container2">
					<div id="m_intro">
						<div>
							<div><img src="/images/intro2.jpg" alt="협회소개 사진" /></div>
							<div class="intro_txt f6">
								<h2 class="f1">
									(사)아태평화교류협회
								</h2>
								<div class="wave_img"></div>
								<strong class="f3">일제 강제동원, 절대 잊어서는 안되는 그날의 기억에 대해...</strong>
								<p>
									사단법인 아태평화교류협회 대일항쟁기 아시아 태평양전쟁 당시 1938~1945년 일제의 국가총동원령에 의해 해외로 강제 동원돼 희생된 유골을 발굴해 국내로 봉환을 위해 설립 되었습니다.
									<br /> 본 협회는 지난 13년 간 희생자 자료를 수집·조사하고 있으며 해외 각지에 흩어져 방치된 유골을 발굴하고 수습해 국내로 봉환하는것에 힘쓰고 있습니다.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div id="m_ico">
						<div>
							<a href="/donation">
								<img src="/images/donation_icon_02-04.png" alt="" />
								<span>후원하기</span>
							</a>
						</div>
						<div>
							<a href="/people-return/process">
								<img src="/images/donation_icon_02-05.png" alt="" />
								<span>유골봉환</span>
							</a>
						</div>
						<div>
							<a href="/promote-house/biz-activity">
								<img src="/images/donation_icon_02-06.png" alt="" />
								<span>홍보관</span>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div id="act">
						<div class="act-block block">
							<div class="act_title">
								<h2 class="f1">협회활동</h2>
								<div class="wave_img"></div>
							</div>
							<div class="board_wrap">

								<%
                           		for(var i=0; i<atActRows.length; i++){
                               		var actItem = atActRows[i];
                            	%>
								<div class="board_data">
									<a href=<%= '/promote-house/company-activity/detail/'+actItem.num %>><img src=<%= actItem.thumb_img %> alt='<%= actItem.title %>'/></a>
									<div class="title">
										<a href=<%= '/promote-house/company-activity/detail/'+actItem.num %>>
											<h3 class="f2"><%= actItem.title %></h3>
											<div class="date f6">
												<%
                                            var originDate = actItem.createdAt.toString();
                                            var dateArray = originDate.split(' ');
                                            var resultDate = dateArray[1]+' '+parseInt(dateArray[2])+', '+dateArray[3];
                                        %>
                                        <%= resultDate %>
											</div>
										</a>
									</div>
									<p class="f6">
										<%
                                var tagedText = actItem.content;
                                var nonTagedText = tagedText.replace(/(<([^>]+)>)/ig,"");
                                var descText;
                                if(nonTagedText.length > 53){
                                    descText = nonTagedText.substr(0, 52)+'...';
                                }else{
                                    descText = nonTagedText;
                                }
                             %><%= descText %>
									</p>
								</div>
								<%
                            	}
                            	%>

							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="patronize">
						<div class="text-block">
							<section>
								<h2 class="f1">역사를 잊은 민족에게<br /> 미래는 없습니다.</h2>
								<div class="wave_img"></div>
								<div class="button">
									<a href="#" class="f3">후원하기</a>
								</div>
							</section>
						</div>
						<div class="img-block">
				            <div></div>
				        </div>
						<div class="img-block2">
				            <div></div>
				        </div>

					</div>

					<!-- 보도자료 부분 -->
					<div id="news">
						<div class="act-block block">
							<div class="act_title">
								<h2 class="f1">보도자료</h2>
								<div class="wave_img"></div>

							</div>
							<div class="board_wrap">
							<%
                            for(var i=0; i<broadcastRows.length; i++){
                                var broadcastItem = broadcastRows[i];
                            %>

								<div class="board_data">
									<a href=<%= '/data/broadcast-data/detail/'+broadcastItem.num %>><img src=<%= broadcastItem.thumb_img %> alt='<%= broadcastItem.title %>' /></a>
									<div class="title">
										<a href=<%= '/data/broadcast-data/detail/'+broadcastItem.num %>>
											<h3 class="f2"><%= broadcastItem.title %></h3>
											<div class="date f6">
												<%
                                                var originDate = broadcastItem.createdAt.toString();
                                                var dateArray = originDate.split(' ');
                                                var resultDate = dateArray[1]+' '+parseInt(dateArray[2])+', '+dateArray[3];
                                            %>
                                            <%= resultDate %>
											</div>
										</a>
									</div>
									<p class="f6"><%
                                var tagedText = broadcastItem.content;
                                var nonTagedText = tagedText.replace(/(<([^>]+)>)/ig,"");
                                var descText;
                                if(nonTagedText.length > 53){
                                    descText = nonTagedText.substr(0, 52)+'...';
                                }else{
                                    descText = nonTagedText;
                                }
                             %><%= descText %></p>
								</div>

 							<%
                            }
                            %>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="main-gallery">
						<div class="detail_photo">
							<div class="photo_table">
								<div class="photo_cell">
									<div class="photo_item">
										<div class="photo">
											<img src="/images/background-sub.jpg" alt="임시" />
										</div>
										<a href="javascript:;"><i class="fa fa-times" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<ul>
							<%
                            for(var i=0; i<galleryRows.length; i++){
                                var galleryItem = galleryRows[i];
                                %>

							<li style="background-image: url(<%= galleryItem.img %>); background-size:cover">
								<a href="javascript:;">
									<i class="fa fa-eye" aria-hidden="true"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<%
                            }
                            %>

						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
